{"title":"各花 TheFlower","date":"2020-07-26T07:13:54.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 26, 2020","L":"07/26/2020","MM-DD":"07-26"},"author":"Birch","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/japan-2014618.webp","link":"2020/07/26/TheFlower","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.496Z","content":"<p>初识时<br>\n一树的合欢火一般烧着<br>\n一阵雨过<br>\n艳得更胜从前</p>\n<p>于是他下了一个月的雨<br>\n终于这花<br>\n都如烟消散<br>\n尽数成泥</p>\n<p>我想桂花是否能挺过这雨<br>\n但已无从得知<br>\n楼下的桂树早已被拔去<br>\n只剩下干瘪的土块<br>\n静静地哀嚎</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Burdensome","link":"2020/07/28/Burdensome"},"next":{"title":"第三幕 冰原的故事","link":"2020/07/18/StoryOfIceField"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/07/26/TheFlower/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"86 words in 1 min"}